Programming
NOTE: A program block can contain more than one G-code, as long as those
G-codes are from different groups. You cannot place two G-codes
from the same group in a program block. Also note that only one
M-code per block is allowed.
%
O40001 (Basic program) ;
(G54 X0 Y0 is top right corner of part) ;
(Z0 is on top of the part) ;
(T1 is a 1/2" end mill) ;
