M08 (Coolant on) ;
(BEGIN CUTTING BLOCKS) ;
G01 F20. Z-0.1 (Feed to cutting depth) ;
X-4. Y-4. (linear motion) ;
(BEGIN COMPLETION BLOCKS) ;
